com.darkfoxdev.tesi.targetlint.checks.operations

Class CheckOperation

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.darkfoxdev.tesi.targetlint.checks.operations.CheckOperation
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    GroupAndExecuteCheckOperation, MatchNumberCheckOperation, ReferenceMatchCheckOperation, TargetFilterAsCheckOperation

    public abstract class CheckOperation
extends java.lang.Object
    The type Check Operation. It's the processing unit of a Check: every check operation takes a list of matches and, through the check(...) method, filters them returning only the relevant ones. Check operations can be chained in series (using and(...) method) or in parallel (using or(...) method).
